{"tid":2224830,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"點解有班人寧願開post推post屌龍門屌渣哥屌misspun屌david屌依個果個都唔肯開post屌支那屌警犬","createTime":"2020-10-01T00:08:02.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-01T04:26:48.000Z","uid":65328,"like":78,"dislike":15,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"c65ff93c9174810fb120c53743688ad81ae36133","tid":2224830,"uid":65328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-01T00:08:02.000Z","msg":"明明支那同警犬係香港人最大敵人， 佢地十惡不赦， 點解有班人寧願開post推post屌龍門屌渣哥屌misspun屌david屌依個果個， 都唔肯開post屌支那屌警犬？<br />\n<br />\n佢地會用成個鐘時間覆幾十個留言解釋點解唔開post屌支那屌警犬， 話&quot;點解要開&quot;/&quot;你又知其他地方無屌&quot;/&quot;開post屌有撚用&quot;, etc<br />\n<br />\n但係開post屌支那屌警犬一分鐘都唔洗， 佢地寧願用成個鐘時間覆幾十個留言兜， <br />\n好矛盾好核突"},{"pid":"761d5231138150909cdb9bcf1208dacf56a6e40c","tid":2224830,"uid":237459,"like":5,"dislike":2,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-01T00:09:41.000Z","msg":"香港人欺善怕惡係咁"},{"pid":"09337f88da80c346ffbd2f0717ff5d741d792877","tid":2224830,"uid":65328,"like":27,"dislike":0,"score":27,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-01T00:09:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mg3N9SJ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fmg3N9SJ.jpg&h=9df44bd5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n發覺連登好多acc同拜登一樣唔敢屌支那屌警犬<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5096e243bfb5142782bdd65b8585a7b170a09924","tid":2224830,"uid":65328,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"761d5231138150909cdb9bcf1208dacf56a6e40c","tid":2224830,"uid":237459,"like":5,"dislike":2,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-01T00:09:41.000Z","msg":"香港人欺善怕惡係咁"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-01T00:13:01.000Z","msg":"我懷疑佢地係五毛/pr/警犬/藍絲， 唔可以開post屌， 因為開過post屌一起底就有哂紀錄， 會收唔到錢/規矩寫明唔俾開/有懲罰/驚第日組織秋後算帳"},{"pid":"5c27d275e408604cebb1b0576280fa711371020a","tid":2224830,"uid":158546,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-01T00:25:08.000Z","msg":"水門渣9<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img